{"tid":1261410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家要小心","createTime":"2019-06-27T08:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T11:38:40.000Z","uid":239919,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ef6edf2d1629e2fea1b5421f41037ec94406e3","tid":1261410,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"出左黎咁多次<br />\n咩都見過晒<br />\n而家啲狗個個都唔係人咁品<br />\n對呢場抗爭黎講 每一個人嘅安全都好重要<br />\n我地呢班大學生 唔想再見到好似9/6圍捕嗰晚咁<br />\n求下大家 衝還衝 睇實即時<br />\n全部都係第一手消息親自落哨 <br />\n求下你地要小心啲<br />\n<br />\n金鐘中環灣仔即時實況目測channel<br />\n&lt;<a href=\"http://t.me/juneforstfuneral&gt;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjuneforstfuneral%3E&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=ecdc1f3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/juneforstfuneral&gt;</a><br />\n<br />\n終點未至，未可中止。<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"4b23e75d2b8b0683b4f2f2720926c1c853075e12","tid":1261410,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"cecb90c94a27ed00fec9b45be60ddeb1cf8de0e0","tid":1261410,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3039e1fe16b671949fbac1f7e428db68a2659cb6","tid":1261410,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ffde16c966027c84a135781a938ce2982b9cb0e4","tid":1261410,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:35:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6177380a23f5d07a42788992c8c361cd9b9e3fe6","tid":1261410,"uid":20348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50933d99123cae6d15b5cacfb9c61ba3aede5c22","tid":1261410,"uid":239919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T08:38:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a8cdb082b534c6963eeed8306249f5a16da